'''威廉·路易斯·"比利"·沙柏'''（{{lang-en|'''William Louis "Billy" Sharp'''}}，{{bd|1986年|2月5日|catIdx=Sharp, Billy}}）出生於[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[谢菲尔德|-{zh-hans:谢菲尔德; zh-hk:錫菲市;}-]]，是一名[[職業|職業]][[足球|足球]][[運動員|運動員]]，司職[[前鋒_(足球)|前鋒]]，現時效力[[英冠|英冠]]球會[[謝菲爾德聯足球俱樂部|錫菲聯]]。

==生平==
===錫菲聯===
沙柏初時參加[[罗瑟勒姆足球俱乐部|洛達咸]]的足球學院，於被棄用後轉投家鄉的[[谢菲尔德联足球俱乐部|錫菲聯]]青訓學院。他於2002年簽署學徒球員合約，雖然在青年隊及預備隊表現出色，卻一直未能打進領隊[[尼爾·禾諾克|尼爾·禾諾克]]（Neil Warnock）的一隊陣容。2004年11月13日沙柏首次代表錫菲聯一隊上陣，於主場1-1賽和[[沃特福德足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:沃特福德; zh-hk:屈福特;}-]]，在完場前後補上陣<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/3988267.stm |title=Sheff Utd 1-1 Watford |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2004-11-13 |accessdate=2010-06-10 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307074555/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/3988267.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2005年1月21日沙柏獲外借到[[英乙|英乙]]爭取保級的[[鲁什登钻石足球俱乐部|魯斯頓鑽石]]一個月汲取上陣經驗<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11683_2324653,00.html |title=Blades slash squad |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2005-01-21 |accessdate=2010-06-10 |archive-date=2016-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309152311/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11683_2324653,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，在上陣4場及射入1球後，於2月15日獲延長借用一個月<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11683_2326942,00.html |title=Diamonds keep Sharp |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2005-02-15 |accessdate=2010-06-10}}</ref>，最終在借用三個月期間上陣16場並射入9球，包括完場前射入致勝球以3-2擊敗本地宿敵[[北安普顿足球俱乐部|諾咸頓]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/4321359.stm |title=Rushden 3-2 Northampton |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2005-03-12 |accessdate=2010-06-10 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307141157/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/4321359.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>及4-2擊敗[[Boston_United_F.C.|波士頓聯]]（Boston United）中大演[[帽子戲法|帽子戲法]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/4427627.stm |title=Rushden 4-2 Boston |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2005-04-16 |accessdate=2010-06-10 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305002020/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/4427627.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並協助球隊成功保級。領隊尼爾·禾諾克警告其他球隊不要動沙柏的腦筋<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11683_2333415,00.html |title=Warnock: We won't sell Billy |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2005-04-23 |accessdate=2010-06-10 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310085036/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11683_2333415,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。沙柏返回錫菲聯於閉幕戰作客對[[伍尔弗汉普顿流浪足球俱乐部|狼隊]]，第二次及最後一次為球隊後補上陣<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/4500853.stm |title=Wolves 4-2 Sheff Utd |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2005-05-08 |accessdate=2010-06-10 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307053437/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/4500853.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===斯肯索普===
2005年7月27日[[英甲|英甲]]升班馬[[斯坎索普联足球俱乐部|斯肯索普]]希望借用沙柏被拒<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11683_2343202,00.html |title=Iron fail with Sharp bid |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2005-07-27 |accessdate=2010-06-10 |archive-date=2016-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309135308/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11683_2343202,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，8月4日兩會達成轉會費協議<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11683_2344356,00.html |title=Iron agree Sharp fee |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2005-08-04 |accessdate=2010-06-10 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308035533/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11683_2344356,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，最初沙柏拒絕離隊<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11683_2344591,00.html |title=Sharp rejects Iron move |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2005-08-08 |accessdate=2010-06-10}}</ref>，直到8月16日他才答應以10萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]身價正式轉投斯肯索普，簽約三年<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11683_2345206,00.html |title=Iron Sharp-en attack |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2005-08-16 |accessdate=2010-06-10 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308012704/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11683_2345206,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。沙柏與同齡的[[安迪·基奧治|安迪·基奧治]]組成最具攻力的鋒線組合，於11月初兩人已合共射入18球，時任領隊[[白賴仁·羅斯|白賴仁·羅斯]]（Brian Laws）表示無意出售兩人<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11725_2354479,00.html |title=Laws won't sell youngsters |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2005-11-12 |accessdate=2010-06-10 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308010625/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11725_2354479,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他迅即成為[[格蘭福特公園|格蘭福特公園]]（Glanford Park）球迷的寵兒，雖然在2006年2月觸傷[[腳踝|腳踝]][[韧带|韧带]]而缺陣6星期<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11725_2367999,00.html |title=Sharp out for six weeks |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2006-02-21 |accessdate=2010-06-16}}</ref>，仍然在加盟首季射入24球。

[[2006年至2007年英格蘭足球甲級聯賽|2006/07年球季]]沙柏在聯賽射入30球，其中在10月份4場聯賽場場均有入球，合共轟入5球，使他獲選「英甲10月份最佳球員」<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/scunthorpe_utd/6118694.stm |title=Iron striker Sharp secures prize |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2006-11-05 |accessdate=2010-06-16 |archive-date=2020-07-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200724065813/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/scunthorpe_utd/6118694.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，最終協助斯肯索普贏得[[英甲|英甲]]聯賽冠軍<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/6578843.stm |title=Blackpool 3-1 Scunthorpe |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2007-04-28 |accessdate=2010-06-16 |archive-date=2019-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190402132540/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/6578843.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並是球會成立以來首次升班到[[英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|次級聯賽]]，亦是英格蘭四個高級聯賽組別中入球最多的一員，並獲選「英甲最佳球員」<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11698_2407397,00.html |title=Koumas takes Championship prize |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2007-03-05 |accessdate=2010-06-16 |archive-date=2016-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309143017/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11698_2407397,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>及「英甲PFA球迷公選足球先生」<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11725_2412018,00.html |title=Sharp shoots to PFA award |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2007-04-24 |accessdate=2010-06-16 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308010713/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11725_2412018,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他於效力斯肯索普兩季合共上陣95場及射入56球。

由於沙柏及拍檔基奧治表現出色，斯肯索普早於冬季[[轉會窗|轉會窗]]已拒絕兩單「大額」收購出價<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11725_2399994,00.html |title=Iron turn down two bids |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2006-12-31 |accessdate=2010-06-15 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310091307/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11725_2399994,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而只餘一年合約在身的沙柏成為各大球會的爭奪目標，其中包括[[英超|英超]]的[[埃弗顿足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:埃弗顿; zh-hk:愛華頓;}-]]、[[富勒姆足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:富勒姆; zh-hk:富咸;}-]]及舊東家[[谢菲尔德联足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:谢菲尔德联; zh-hk:錫菲聯;}-]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11725_2411439,00.html |title=Iron aim to keep Sharp |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2007-04-17 |accessdate=2010-06-16 |archive-date=2016-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309161715/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11725_2411439,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。建基於他的超強入球能力，可以預見其他球會對他有興趣，於球季結束後多支球隊競逐出價收購<ref name="Sharp must make decision on Owls">{{cite news | language = en | title = Sharp must make decision on Owls | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/scunthorpe_utd/6656749.stm | publisher = ''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' | date = 2007-05-15 | accessdate = 2007-05-15 | archive-date = 2007-09-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070909143846/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/scunthorpe_utd/6656749.stm | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="Iron reject Owls offer for Sharp">{{cite news | language = en | title = Iron reject Owls offer for Sharp | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/scunthorpe_utd/6656749.stm | publisher = ''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' | date = 2007-05-16 | accessdate = 2007-05-16 | archive-date = 2007-09-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070909143846/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/scunthorpe_utd/6656749.stm | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="Iron confirm Norwich's Sharp bid">{{cite news | language = en | title = Iron confirm Norwich's Sharp bid | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/n/norwich/6701663.stm | publisher = ''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' | date = 2007-05-29 | accessdate = 2007-05-29 | archive-date = 2007-08-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070827063223/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/n/norwich/6701663.stm | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="Preston confirm interest in Sharp">{{cite news |language=en | title = Preston confirm interest in Sharp | url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/p/preston/6672551.stm | publisher = ''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' | date = 2007-05-19 | accessdate = 2007-05-19}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | language = en | title = Sharp in talks with Norwich | url = http://www.pinkun.com/content/ncfc/story.aspx?brand=PINKUNOnline&category=Norwich&tBrand=PinkUnOnline&tCategory=Norwich&itemid=NOED20%20Jun%202007%2012%3A21%3A57%3A380 | publisher = ''The Pink 'Un'' | date = 2007-06-20 | accessdate = 2007-06-20 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070928090515/http://www.pinkun.com/content/ncfc/story.aspx?brand=PINKUNOnline&category=Norwich&tBrand=PinkUnOnline&tCategory=Norwich&itemid=NOED20%20Jun%202007%2012:21:57:380 | archivedate = 2007-09-28 }}</ref>。

===重返錫菲聯===
2007年7月4日沙柏重投舊東家[[谢菲尔德联足球俱乐部|錫菲聯]]，轉會費200萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]，同時[[乔纳森·福特|-{zh-hans:乔纳森·福特; zh-hk:科迪;}-]]（Jonathan Forte）則由錫菲聯加盟[[斯坎索普联足球俱乐部|斯肯索普]]，他獲發背號「24」的球衣<ref name="Sharp gets Blades' return ticket">{{cite news | language = en | title = Sharp gets Blades' return ticket | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/sheff_utd/6249576.stm | publisher = ''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' | date = 4 July 2007 | accessdate = 4 July 2007 | archive-date = 2007-08-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070818084246/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/sheff_utd/6249576.stm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[2007年至2008年英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|2007/08年球季]]揭幕戰於主場2-2賽和[[科尔切斯特联足球俱乐部|高車士打]]，是沙柏首場為錫菲聯一隊正選上陣<ref name="Sheff Utd 2-2 Colchester">{{cite news |language=en | title = Sheff Utd 2-2 Colchester | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/6931101.stm | publisher = ''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' | date = 2007-08-11 | accessdate = 2007-11-09}}</ref>；並於9月在[[英格蘭聯賽盃|英格蘭聯賽盃]]第三圈5-0大勝[[摩尔甘比足球俱乐部|摩甘比]]取得回歸後首兩個入球<ref name="Sheff Utd 5-0 Morecambe' return ticket">{{cite news |language=en | title = Sheff Utd 5-0 Morecambe | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/league_cup/7008014.stm | publisher = ''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' | date = 2007-09-25 | accessdate = 2007-11-09}}</ref>，但要一直等到翌年3月，主場2-1擊敗[[考文垂足球俱乐部|高雲地利]]才射入首個聯賽入球<ref name="Sheff Utd 2-1 Coventry City">{{cite news |language=en | title = Sheff Utd 2-1 Coventry | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/7285092.stm | publisher = ''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' | date = 2008-11-03 | accessdate = 2008-11-03}}</ref>，取得零的突破後，他於球季結束前再取得3個入球。 

沙柏在[[2008年至2009年英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|2008/09年球季]]有良好開端，於首場主場賽事對[[女王公园巡游者足球俱乐部|昆士柏流浪]]取得一個完美的[[帽子戲法|帽子戲法]]，包括以頭頂、左及右腳射球入網；數星期後對[[考文垂足球俱乐部|高雲地利]]他再射入1球為球隊扳平1-1，但這成為他本季在聯賽最後一個入球。沙柏在其後舉行的[[英格蘭足總盃|英格蘭足總盃]]再射入兩球，包括第五圈重賽對[[赫尔城足球俱乐部|侯城]]有1球進帳，同場他被球證[[彼得·禾頓|禾頓]]誤判[[插水_(足球術語)|插水]]而[[黃牌|記名]]，賽後禾頓為錯誤致歉<ref name="hull red card">{{cite news | language = en | title = Referee apologises for Hull goal | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/sheff_utd/7915275.stm | publisher = ''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' | date = 2009-02-27 | accessdate = 2009-07-30 | archive-date = 2009-03-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090302073116/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/sheff_utd/7915275.stm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。錫菲聯在季後升班附加賽決賽負於[[伯恩利足球俱乐部|般尼]]後展開重組，2009年7月沙柏遭球會掛牌出售<ref name="transfer listed">{{cite news |language=en | title = Sharp put on Blades transfer list | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/sheff_utd/8173816.stm | publisher = ''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' | date = 2009-07-29 | accessdate = 2009-07-30}}</ref>。

2009年整個夏季沙柏不斷被傳會轉投[[唐卡斯特流浪足球俱乐部|唐卡士打]]或[[諾士郡足球會|諾士郡]]，他在[[轉會窗|轉會窗]]關閉前獲外借到唐卡士打一個球季<ref name="donny loan">{{cite news |language=en | title = Doncaster bring in Sharp on loan | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/d/doncaster/8232556.stm | publisher = ''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' | date = 2009-09-01 | accessdate = 2009-09-01}}</ref>。9月26日他在對舊東家[[斯坎索普联足球俱乐部|斯肯索普]]時射入加盟後首球；他的入球陸續有來，於12月已累計10個入球，成為唐卡士打球迷的寵兒，整季上陣35場射入15球，於球季結束後唐卡士打正式將沙柏收歸旗下。

===唐卡士打===
2010年7月7日沙柏以破球會轉會費紀錄的115萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]正式加盟[[唐卡斯特流浪足球俱乐部|唐卡士打]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/d/doncaster/8789155.stm |title=Doncaster Rovers sign Sheffield United's Billy Sharp |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-07-07 |accessdate=2010-07-08 |archive-date=2011-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110208131419/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/d/doncaster/8789155.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他於開季後第二場聯賽射入正式加盟後的首個入球，在主場1-1賽和[[布里斯托尔城足球俱乐部|布里斯托城]]於完場前憑[[十二碼|十二碼]]建功<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/8901710.stm |title=Doncaster 1-1 Bristol City |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-08-14 |accessdate=2010-12-10 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307181151/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/8901710.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。直到10月23日主場2-0擊敗舊東家[[谢菲尔德联足球俱乐部|錫菲聯]]所入的一球<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/9103761.stm |title=Doncaster 2-0 Sheff Utd |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-10-23 |accessdate=2010-12-10 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310075131/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/9103761.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，已累計射入6球，但他在這場賽事拉傷[[腿後腱|腿筋]]，需要缺陣6星期<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/d/doncaster/9125793.stm |title=Billy Sharp injury blow for Doncaster Rovers |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-10-25 |accessdate=2010-12-10 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307055210/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/d/doncaster/9125793.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===修咸頓===
雖然沙柏轉投[[莱斯特城足球俱乐部|莱斯特城]]的交易告吹，但他於2012年1月30日加盟另一支[[英冠|英冠]]爭取升班的球隊[[南安普顿足球俱乐部|修咸頓]]，簽約三年半，與舊上司[[尼祖·艾堅斯|尼祖·艾堅斯]]再續前緣<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/16794210.stm |title=Billy Sharp joins Southampton from Donacaster |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2012-01-30 |accessdate=2012-01-31 |archive-date=2012-01-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120131111811/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/16794210.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2012年8月31日，[[英冠|英冠]]球隊[[诺丁汉森林足球俱乐部|诺丁汉森林]]向修咸頓借用沙柏，為期一個球季<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/19442448 |title=Nottingham Forest sign Billy Sharp and James Coppinger on loan |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2012-08-31 |accessdate=2014-12-17 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924191305/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/19442448 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2013年8月31日，[[英冠|英冠]]球隊[[雷丁足球俱乐部|雷丁]]借用沙柏，至2014年1月，其再一次與時任[[雷丁足球俱乐部|雷丁]]領隊[[尼祖·艾堅斯|尼祖·艾堅斯]]合作<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/24187835 |title=Billy Sharp: Reading sign Southampton striker on loan |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2013-08-31 |accessdate=2014-12-17 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924193922/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/24187835 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2014年1月22日，沙柏以借將身份重返唐卡士打直至球季結朿<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/25844980 |title=Transfer window: Billy Sharp joins Doncaster from Southampton |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2014-01-22 |accessdate=2014-12-17 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924201150/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/25844980 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===列斯聯===
2014年8月13日，28歲的沙柏從修咸頓轉投[[英冠|英冠]]球隊[[列斯聯|列斯聯]]，轉會費金額沒有透露，合約為期兩年<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/28773181 |title=Leeds United sign Southampton striker Billy Sharp |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2014-08-13 |accessdate=2014-12-17 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924211040/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/28773181 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===錫菲聯===
效力一季後，全季入球數量不如人意，轉會至家鄉球會、[[英甲|英甲]]的[[錫菲聯|錫菲聯]]，表現出色，入球量出眾，更助球會闊別6年終重返英冠聯賽，繼續衝擊英超之夢。升上[[英冠|英冠]]後，沙柏表現依舊出色，助球隊一度進佔榜首。2018/19年度球季，錫菲聯取得英冠亞軍，來季升上英超比賽。

